loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$k = random(3,9,1);$k2=2*$k;
$h = random(3,9,1);$h2=2*$h;
$r = random(1,1.4*sqrt($k**2+$h**2),1);
$c = $k**2+$h**2-$r**2;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\( x^2+y^2-$h2 x+$k2 y +$c=0 \) is the equation of a circle with center \( (h,k) \) and radius \( r \) for:$BR
$BR
\( h= \)\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $h;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and$BR
\( k= \) \{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  -$k;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and$BR
\( r= \) \{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $r;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
